description: Earth astronauts Richards and Hoagland are on a pioneering mission: they will be the first representatives of Planet Earth to enter into the Sirius Galaxy…a galaxy known for having the most advanced races in all the cosmos. But during an unscheduled stop on an alien world along the way, Richards and Hoagland stumble across an alien race performing a barbaric, ritualistic sacrifice. As they argue over how to proceed, a native dinosaur starts destroying their spaceship. Richards and Hoagland are forced to make an emergency decision, but as with every choice, what will the consequences of their actions be?
name: How Far We Have Come

description: As he is throwing down with a set of Combat Bots trying to apprehend him, Cease-Fire has a vision from the past of the world’s greatest hero, Casimir, failing to stop a giant meteor from colliding with and damaging the planet…the same incident that led to the rise of the robots on earth. After dealing with the robots, Cease-Fire seeks council with Rainey, a medical officer at the human refugee colony in hopes of getting some answers of why he’s struggling with foreign thoughts and ideas in his head. All while the intentions of the robot leader known as Gear Head are becoming more and more clear…
